            <para>
              <text>Section 83 is amended by omitting <amend.in quote="1">an electricity lines business and an electricity supply business that do not have ownership separation</amend.in> and substituting <amend.in quote="1">businesses to which <changeable><citation jurisdiction="nz">section 17D and 17E</citation></changeable> (corporate separation and arm’s-length rules) apply</amend.in>.</text>
            </para>
          </subprov>
        </prov.body>
